data.description: Just Imagine coming home to this Classical Vintage Home. You are going to love the updates as you relax on the New Back Deck, entertaining your guests in the Game Room or Formal Dining Room!  With 3 Bathrooms, everyone has their own private space, and just a minute away from Historical Covington Town Square!  This Lovely home also has an Office, Sunroom, Fenced in Back yard, and covered front porch...so much room!  Kitchen Island with New Appliances, Ask for the list of updates.. Blue Oval 27min
